{
  "stem": "428.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, it was 1948. 19-- what am I talking? 1988, 1988.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yeah, I had four bypass operations, sure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you were telling me about your wife before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Is there anything else that you want to-- to let us know about her and your life together?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well-- well, she-- well, she-- she-- when-- she was born with a spot on the lungs, with a spot on the lungs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So going to the United States, they made that x-rays and everything, and they saw that spot on the lungs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they wanted-- they want to send her back for six months and make another picture in six months later.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It ?] [? was ?] [? on ?] the same thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If it's not worse, [? if it's ?] [? not ?] better, it means it's all right.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But somehow-- somehow-- somehow I push her through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when we came-- before we went on the boat in Bremenhaven in Germany, they separated us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She goes separate, and I went separate to sleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had with me $200, leaving Germany to the United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So when I come up looking for her, well, she's-- she's sitting in a little bed and crying with gypsy women there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She cries, look where I am.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I find there somebody, what they told me, for money, you could get a separate room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a guy who took care of the rooms, and then everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I ask him, how much is going to cost me for a separate room for myself and my wife?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he told me, $30, something like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he have $30, I got a separate room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they used-- used-- we used to be there two weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
